<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٧٢٦ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ , عَنْ قَتَادَةَ فِي رَجُلٍ حَلَفَ كَاذِبًا لَمْ يَكُنْ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«هُوَ أَعْظَمُ مِنَ الْكَفَّارَةِ»</span> عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗٢٤⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٧٢٧ - عَنْ مَعْمَرٍ <span class="c2">«وَأَنَا أَرَى فِيهِ الْكَفَّارَةَ وَيَتُوبُ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>